name: 3rd International Conference on Applied Science and Engineering
content: The 3rd International Conference on Applied Science and Engineering is going to be held during October 23-24, 2023 at Bangkok, Thailand, which unites a one of a kind and worldwide blend of eminent and important engineers, biotech and symptomatic or diagnostic organizations, leading universities and research companies making the meeting an ideal stage to share understanding, encourage coordinated efforts crosswise over industry and the scholarly community, and assess rising advancements over the globe
